<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Quotes</title>
    <style>
        /* Same styles as index.astro */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #fff;
            color: #101010;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 20px 40px;
            z-index: 100;
        }
        
        .nav-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #666;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        
        .nav-links a:hover,
        .nav-links a.active {
            color: #000;
        }
        
        main {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 140px 40px 80px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 60px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        
        .content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        footer {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-inner">
            <a href="/" class="logo">Chris Price</a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/portfolio" class="active">Portfolio</a></li>
                <li><a href="/books">Books</a></li>
                <li><a href="/quotes">Quotes</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
    
    <main>
    <h1>Quotes</h1>
    <h3>...as I remember them </h3>
    <div class="content">
        <ul>
            <li>You'd sacrifice me for an epithet Harry. - Oscar Wilde (Picture of Dorian Grey)</li>
            <li>I have no need for a noble minded soul. What I need is an accomplice. - Jean Paul Sartre (The Flies)</li>
            <li>It is an ideal state of affairs when the victim rejoices at being led to the slaughter. - Fydor Doystevsky (The Gambler)</li>
            <li>...And on the pedestal these words appeared. My name is Ozymandias, king of kings, look on my works and despair. Nothing besides remains, round the decay 
            of that colosal wreck, boundles and bare. The lone and level sands stretch far away. - Percy Shell (Ozymandias)</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        Â© 2025 Chris Price
    </footer>
</body>
</html>